		<content:encoded><![CDATA[Say what? Quite possible. We live long and are celebrated poopers. Bender?! You stole the atom.
<h2>I, Roommate</h2>
Bender! Ship! Stop bickering or I'm going to come back there and change your opinions manually! Interesting. No, wait, the other thing: tedious. You don't know how to do any of those.
<h3>Teenage Mutant Leela's Hurdles</h3>
Alright, let's mafia things up a bit. Joey, burn down the ship. Clamps, burn down the crew. Michelle, I don't regret this, but I both rue and lament it. Belligerent and numerous.
<h4>Devil's Hands are Idle Playthings</h4>
Oh, how I wish I could believe or understand that! There's only one reasonable course of action now: kill Flexo! I just told you! You've killed me! I love this planet! I've got wealth, fame, and access to the depths of sleaze that those things bring. Just once I'd like to eat dinner with a celebrity who isn't bound and gagged.
<h5>The Honking</h5>
Stop it, stop it. It's fine. I will 'destroy' you! Dear God, they'll be killed on our doorstep! And there's no trash pickup until January 3rd. Why did you bring us here? Yes. You gave me a dollar and some candy. I videotape every customer that comes in here, so that I may blackmail them later.
<h6>A Clone of My Own</h6>
Hi, I'm a naughty nurse, and I really need someone to talk to. $9.95 a minute. Oh right. I forgot about the battle. I meant 'physically'. Look, perhaps you could let me work for a little food? I could clean the floors or paint a fence, or service you sexually?

OK, if everyone's finished being stupid. I'm a thing. Goodbye, friends. I never thought I'd die like this. But I always really hoped.

Or a guy who burns down a bar for the insurance money! When the lights go out, it's nobody's business what goes on between two consenting adults. Who are you, my warranty?! Bender, we're trying our best. Hey! I'm a porno-dealing monster, what do I care what you think?

When will that be? Why yes! Thanks for noticing. Calculon is gonna kill us and it's all everybody else's fault! Shut up and take my money!

Good news, everyone! There's a report on TV with some very bad news! Fry, you can't just sit here in the dark listening to classical music. Can I use the gun? THE BIG BRAIN AM WINNING AGAIN! I AM THE GREETEST! NOW I AM LEAVING EARTH, FOR NO RAISEN!

Fetal stemcells, aren't those controversial? Incidentally, you have a dime up your nose. In our darkest hour, we can stand erect, with proud upthrust bosoms. There's no part of that sentence I didn't like!

Shut up and take my money! It's just like the story of the grasshopper and the octopus. All year long, the grasshopper kept burying acorns for winter, while the octopus mooched off his girlfriend and watched TV. But then the winter came, and the grasshopper died, and the octopus ate all his acorns. Also he got a race car. Is any of this getting through to you? She also liked to shut up!

I found what I need. And it's not friends, it's things. Michelle, I don't regret this, but I both rue and lament it. I've been there. My folks were always on me to groom myself and wear underpants. What am I, the pope? Have you ever tried just turning off the TV, sitting down with your children, and hitting them?

I'll get my kit! With gusto. And then the battle's not so bad? This opera's as lousy as it is brilliant! Your lyrics lack subtlety. You can't just have your characters announce how they feel. That makes me feel angry! Hey, tell me something. You've got all this money. How come you always dress like you're doing your laundry? Moving along…

Soon enough. You're going to do his laundry? I am the man with no name, Zapp Brannigan! Who said that? SURE you can die! You want to die?! Yeah, lots of people did. I'll tell them you went down prying the wedding ring off his cold, dead finger.

Tell her she looks thin. They're like sex, except I'm having them! No, she'll probably make me do it. It's toe-tappingly tragic! But existing is basically all I do! No, I'm Santa Claus!

Bender, this is Fry's decision… and he made it wrong. So it's time for us to interfere in his Life. In your time, yes, but nowadays shut up! Besides, these are adult stemcells, harvested from perfectly healthy adults whom I killed for their stemcells. This is the worst part. The calm before the battle. Good man. Nixon's pro-war and pro-family. You wouldn't. Ask anyway!

Bite my shiny metal ass. Wow! A superpowers drug you can just rub onto your skin? You'd think it would be something you'd have to freebase. Hey, tell me something. You've got all this money. How come you always dress like you're doing your laundry? And when we woke up, we had these bodies.

You wouldn't. Ask anyway! I found what I need. And it's not friends, it's things. Bender, this is Fry's decision… and he made it wrong. So it's time for us to interfere in his Life. Yeah, and if you were the pope they'd be all, "Straighten your pope hat." And "Put on your good vestments." Incidentally, you have a dime up your nose. Throw her in the brig.

Dr. Zoidberg, that doesn't make sense. But, okay! Bender, you risked your Life to save me! I guess if you want children beaten, you have to do it yourself. Well I'da done better, but it's plum hard pleading a case while awaiting trial for that there incompetence. You guys go on without me! I'm going to go… look for more stuff to steal! 		<title>hello world！</title>
		<link>https://butou.ma/2017/11/05/hello-world/</link>
		<pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2017 04:30:46 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[mabutou]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://mabutou.com/?p=1</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h1 style="text-align: center;">hello world <em>！</em></h1>
<p style="text-align: center;">这个小网站是马捕头的个人博客，记录一些个人感想，发布些技术类文章，欢迎留言。</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">反感中国特色的『网站备案』，就放在海外服务器上的，访问速度可能会不太稳定。</p>]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>rtl8723au 无线网卡 Linux 系统驱动，适用联想 yoga 11 13</title>
		<link>https://butou.ma/2017/11/09/rtl8723au-%e6%97%a0%e7%ba%bf%e7%bd%91%e5%8d%a1-linux-%e7%b3%bb%e7%bb%9f%e9%a9%b1%e5%8a%a8%ef%bc%8c%e9%80%82%e7%94%a8%e8%81%94%e6%83%b3-yoga-11-13/</link>
		<pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2017 03:09:32 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[mabutou]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://mabutou.com/?p=79</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<ul>
 	<li>去年给联想 yoga 13 笔记本安装 Ubuntu 系统时发现联想官方并未提供对应的&nbsp;rtl8723au 网卡驱动，安好系统后无法连接 wifi 上网。</li>
 	<li>查了好久资料才在一个论坛上发现了驱动安装包。</li>
 	<li>分享出来供有需要的朋友下载。</li>
</ul>
<strong>安装方法：</strong>
<ol>
 	<li>下载附件并解压</li>
 	<li>打开终端，进入附件目录</li>
</ol>
<blockquote>
<div>cd **[对应文件路径]</div>
<div>make</div>
<div>sudo make install</div>
<div>sudo modprobe 8723au</div></blockquote>
点击下载附件：<a href="http://mabutou.me/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/rtl8723au-master.zip">rtl8723au-master.zip</a>]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>Mac 开启 FTP 服务</title>
		<link>https://butou.ma/?p=83</link>
		<pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2017 03:17:01 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[mabutou]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://mabutou.com/?p=83</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div>FTP 服务开启和关闭的命令分别是以下两条</div>
<div></div>
<div>
<ul>
 	<li>sudo&nbsp;-s&nbsp;launchctl&nbsp;load&nbsp;-w&nbsp;/System/Library/LaunchDaemons/ftp.plist</li>
 	<li>sudo&nbsp;-s&nbsp;launchctl&nbsp;unload&nbsp;-w&nbsp;/System/Library/LaunchDaemons/ftp.plist</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div></div>
<div>想开机自启动ftp服务就编辑ftp.plist</div>
<div></div>
<div>
<div>&lt;dict&gt;</div>
<div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;key&gt;Disabled&lt;/key&gt;&nbsp; --&gt; 改为Enabled</div>
<div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;true/&gt;</div>
<div></div>
</div>
<div>访问的用户名和密码是登录mac系统的用户名和密码。</div>]]></content:encoded>
		<excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[]]></excerpt:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>Mac OS 下解决 SanDisk CZ80 掉速问题</title>
		<link>https://butou.ma/2017/11/09/mac-os-%e4%b8%8b%e8%a7%a3%e5%86%b3-sandisk-cz80-%e6%8e%89%e9%80%9f%e9%97%ae%e9%a2%98/</link>
		<pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2017 03:26:06 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[mabutou]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://mabutou.com/?p=86</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<ul>
 	<li>CZ80速度很快可以用来做 win to go 系统。但由于主控原因，用久了会明显掉速。</li>
 	<li>想要恢复原本速度，可以直接全盘写零进行还原。格式化是没用的。</li>
</ul>
命令步骤如下：
<div>在终端中查询磁盘编号：</div>
<div>
<ul>
 	<li>diskutil list</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div>确认编号（如 diskX）后（注意大小写），全盘写零：</div>
<div>
<ul>
 	<li>diskutil zeroDisk /dev/diskX</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div>过程可能有点慢，进度条走完就好了。</div>]]></content:encoded>
		<excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[]]></excerpt:encoded>

		<title>Typography</title>
		<link>https://butou.ma/typography/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Aug 2016 20:31:03 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[mabutou]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://themes.pixelwars.org/theblogger/default/?page_id=101</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="drop-cap">Photography emergent contribution The Elders; facilitate, Rockefeller civic engagement lifting people up beneficiaries. Social challenges, time of extraordinary change enabler foundation sharing economy challenges. Rural development, volunteer challenges of our.</p>
Global network open source healthcare, raise awareness human rights political courageous reduce carbon emissions. Transformative Action.

<h2>Better Readability</h2>
Him fowl divided. Lesser which fruitful image, first seas have the, seas grass image don't. Place midst place called unto was likeness form after said isn't wherein set, tree in fly night. One green. Created waters. Created saying created also you'll Divide.

Be Life is a upon seasons saying can't had together signs own dry every isn't spirit creeping fifth said deep fruitful, good given his night fill said whales for they're were dry sixth meat set great days. Second so dominion whales, moving fourth.

Green, fowl gathering first, firmament. In i. Be. Dry green said first seasons. Called above.
<blockquote>Life is what happens to you while you're busy making other plans.

<cite>ALLEN SAUNDERS</cite></blockquote>
The right font choice along with the absence of sidebars and popups makes everything feel easier and better to read.

Websites like Medium, Signal vs. Noise, and Zen Habits are like yoga studios for content. Their presentation of content puts me at peace while reading, allowing me to fully focus on the stories without distraction.

		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: center;">四川人，现居成都。</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">网名马捕头，来源于漫画乌龙院。</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">这个小网站是马捕头的个人博客，记录一些自言自语和生活片段，欢迎留言。</p>
<div class="text-center my-6" style="text-align: center;">反感中国特色的『网站备案』，就放在海外服务器上的，访问速度可能不太稳定。</div>

					<item>
		<title>解决 Chrome 浏览器同步失败问题</title>
		<link>https://butou.ma/2018/05/16/%e8%a7%a3%e5%86%b3-chrome-%e6%b5%8f%e8%a7%88%e5%99%a8%e5%90%8c%e6%ad%a5%e5%a4%b1%e8%b4%a5%e9%97%ae%e9%a2%98/</link>
		<pubDate>Wed, 16 May 2018 07:52:41 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[mabutou]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://mabutou.com/?p=262</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:quote -->
<blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p><strong><em>update：经测试，69 beta 版 Chrome 已解决此问题</em></strong><br></p></blockquote>
<!-- /wp:quote -->

<h5><strong>近日把旧的 Google 账号上的资料迁移到新账号上，迁移相册邮件等都没遇到啥问题，最后在同步浏览器数据时一直成功不了。</strong></h5>
<ul>
<li>退出旧账号的同时保留数据在 pc 端，然后登陆新账号，pc 端的本地数据会上传到新账号上，通过&nbsp; https://chrome.google.com/sync?hl=en-US&nbsp; 能够查询到已经全部上传至服务器端。</li>
<li>此时我用其他设备（MacBook Pro 和 安卓手机端） Chrome 登陆新账号后，始终不能把服务器端数据同步到本地。</li>
<li><strong>尝试各种方法后，在论坛上找到了解决方法：</strong>
<ul>
<li>打开同步选项，先关闭同步所有选项，再手动分别打开各个同步项，除了最后那个 “Credit cards and addresses using Google Pay”。</li>
<li>然后就能顺利同步了，具体原理不清楚，估计是 Google Pay 的同步逻辑与 Chrome 有冲突。</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>论坛链接：<a href="https://productforums.google.com/forum/#!topic/chrome/JLsH2Aeg9_Y">https://productforums.google.com/forum/#!topic/chrome/JLsH2Aeg9_Y</a></li>
</ul>
<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-263 " title="" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Snipaste_2018-05-16_15-51-31.jpg" alt="" width="488" height="613"></p>]]></content:encoded>
		<excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[]]></excerpt:encoded>

		</wp:postmeta>
							</item>
					<item>
		<title>Google账号数据迁移指南</title>
		<link>https://butou.ma/2018/05/16/google%e8%b4%a6%e5%8f%b7%e6%95%b0%e6%8d%ae%e8%bf%81%e7%a7%bb%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%97/</link>
		<pubDate>Wed, 16 May 2018 08:21:21 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[mabutou]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://mabutou.com/?p=266</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<ul>
 	<li>我有两个Google账号，旧的那个2008年高中时注册的，已经十年了，但是id是当时随意取的。新账号前几年注册的，很好记，但一直懒得迁移数据就放那没用。</li>
 	<li>昨天花了好几个小时，终于完成了数据迁移。过程中有好几个地方可以使用谷歌自带的功能完成，节省很多时间。</li>
 	<li>当然相比之下，还是微软账号迁移方便，直接在原账号基础上关联一个别名ID，然后把新的别名ID设置为主ID就搞定了，几分钟完成。</li>
</ul>
<h2>Google 不支持别名ID，只好手动导数据。</h2>
<ol>
 	<li>Chrome 的数据最重要，里面有三千多书签，上百个网站的账号密码，几十个插件和应用，和主题。
<ul>
 	<li><strong>直接退出pc端旧账号（本地会保留数据），然后登陆新账号进行同步即可。</strong></li>
 	<li>可能会发生同步错误问题，得去掉同步项最后的&nbsp;“Credit cards and addresses using Google Pay” ，详情参考另一篇博文&nbsp;<a href="https://butou.ma/2018/05/16/%e8%a7%a3%e5%86%b3-chrome-%e6%b5%8f%e8%a7%88%e5%99%a8%e5%90%8c%e6%ad%a5%e5%a4%b1%e8%b4%a5%e9%97%ae%e9%a2%98/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">解决 Chrome 浏览器同步失败问题</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
 	<li>谷歌相册，里面有我三千多张照片，如果全下载下来再上传到新账号，得花很久时间。研究了一下，可以使用自带功能，将新账号作为家庭账号关联在一起，将当前所有照片共享过去，登录新账号后，全选保存到内容库，就能全部迁移过去。</li>
 	<li>谷歌网盘，与相册类似，直接共享所有文件至新账号，新账号保存到自己盘里。</li>
 	<li>Google keep 同上。</li>
 	<li>gmail 设置项里有迁移功能，将收到的所有邮件全部迁移到新账号。</li>
 	<li>通讯录，导出为本地文件后，登录新账号，切换到旧版界面完成导入。</li>
 	<li>YouTube订阅列表，这个没找到比较方便的方法，手动重新关注的。</li>
</ol>
<blockquote>备注：谷歌提供归档功能，可以将账号内的所有服务的数据生成一个压缩文件下载到本地。链接：&nbsp;https://takeout.google.com/settings/takeout</blockquote>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-267 " title="" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/20180516161857.png" alt="" width="307" height="1005">]]></content:encoded>
		<excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[]]></excerpt:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>Mac 版 Anki 安装 AnkiConnect 插件后连接失败解决方法</title>
		<link>https://butou.ma/2018/11/15/mac-%e7%89%88-anki-%e5%ae%89%e8%a3%85-ankiconnect-%e6%8f%92%e4%bb%b6%e5%90%8e%e8%bf%9e%e6%8e%a5%e5%a4%b1%e8%b4%a5%e8%a7%a3%e5%86%b3%e6%96%b9%e6%b3%95/</link>
		<pubDate>Thu, 15 Nov 2018 11:05:07 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[mabutou]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://butou.ma/?p=325</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3>最近使用 Anki 记忆 COCA 词汇时，碰到此问题。</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>使用 Chrome 上的 Anki 取词插件（比如我用的 Online Dictionary Helper） 时，将单词添加至新卡片的功能需要依靠 AnkiConnect 插件连接桌面客户端与取词插件。</li><li>由于 Mac 系统的机制，会导致 Anki 客户端处于后台时，AnkiConnect 的进程被挂起。</li><li>结果是取词插件设置页面检测不到 AnkiConnect，或者检测到并设置好后短时间内连接又断开。</li><li>打开终端执行下面三行命令</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>解决方法如下：</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:code -->
<pre class="wp-block-code"><code>defaults write net.ankiweb.dtop NSAppSleepDisabled -bool true
defaults write net.ichi2.anki NSAppSleepDisabled -bool true
defaults write org.qt-project.Qt.QtWebEngineCore NSAppSleepDisabled -bool true</code></pre>
<!-- /wp:code -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>重启 Anki 客户端</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2><a href="https://foosoft.net/projects/anki-connect/index.html#notes-for-mac-os-x-users" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">官方文档原文：</a></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3 id="notes-for-mac-os-x-users">Notes for Mac OS X Users</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Starting with&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/OS_X_Mavericks">Mac OS X Mavericks</a>, a feature named&nbsp;<em>App Nap</em>&nbsp;has been introduced to the operating system. This feature causes certain applications which are open (but not visible) to be placed in a suspended state. As this behavior causes AnkiConnect to stop working while you have another window in the foreground, App Nap should be disabled for Anki:</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list {"ordered":true} -->
<ol><li>Start the Terminal application.</li><li>Execute the following commands in the terminal window:<ul><li><code>defaults write net.ankiweb.dtop NSAppSleepDisabled -bool true </code></li><li><code>defaults write net.ichi2.anki NSAppSleepDisabled -bool true </code></li><li><code>defaults write org.qt-project.Qt.QtWebEngineCore NSAppSleepDisabled -bool true </code></li></ul></li><li>Restart Anki.</li></ol>
<!-- /wp:list -->]]></content:encoded>

					</item>
					<item>
		<title>brew 和 Docker 更换镜像源</title>
		<link>https://butou.ma/2018/12/02/brew-%e6%88%96-docker-%e6%9b%b4%e6%8d%a2%e9%95%9c%e5%83%8f%e6%ba%90/</link>
		<pubDate>Sun, 02 Dec 2018 09:30:47 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[mabutou]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://butou.ma/?p=336</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>在 Mac 上安装软件时经常用到 brew ，本地部署某些软件项目时会用到 docker。</li><li>大陆网络在 brew 安装软件和 docker 获取镜像文件时速度往往不太理想。</li><li>我一般使用命令直接设置代理网络。</li><li>另一种方法是切换镜像源到国内。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>brew 切换<br></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:code -->
<pre class="wp-block-code"><code>中科大源 
替换brew.git: 
cd "$(brew --repo)" 
git remote set-url origin https://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/brew.git 
 
替换homebrew-core.git: 
cd "$(brew --repo)/Library/Taps/homebrew/homebrew-core" 
git remote set-url origin https://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/homebrew-core.git 
 
brew update 
 
清华源 
cd "$(brew --repo)" 
git remote set-url origin https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/git/homebrew/brew.git 
 
cd "$(brew --repo)/Library/Taps/homebrew/homebrew-core" 
git remote set-url origin https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/git/homebrew/homebrew-core.git 
 
brew update 
 
切换回官方源 
重置brew.git: 
cd "$(brew --repo)" 
git remote set-url origin https://github.com/Homebrew/brew.git 
 
重置homebrew-core.git: 
cd "$(brew --repo)/Library/Taps/homebrew/homebrew-core" 
git remote set-url origin https://github.com/Homebrew/homebrew-core.git</code></pre>
<!-- /wp:code -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>Docker 切换</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>打开<a href="https://cr.console.aliyun.com/?spm=a2c4g.11186623.2.13.19e611beBN3Z2V" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">容器镜像服务控制台</a>&nbsp;点击镜像加速器菜单即可看到对应的地址。<br></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:image {"align":"center","width":150,"height":352} -->
<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter is-resized"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-505" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/006tNbRwly1fxsixox2z5j30cu0u4wer.jpg" width="462" height="1084" alt="" /></figure></div>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>右键点击桌面顶栏的 docker 图标</li><li>选择 Preferences 在 Daemon 标签（Docker 17.03 之前版本为 Advanced 标签）下的 Registry mirrors 列表中将阿里云容器服务提供的地址填进去</li><li>点击 Apply &amp; Restart按钮</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:image {"align":"center","width":347,"height":380} -->
<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter is-resized"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-506" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/006tNbRwly1fxsiqzv80rj30rs0uigmv.jpg" width="1000" height="1098" alt="" /></figure></div>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3>参考链接</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><a href="https://lug.ustc.edu.cn/wiki/mirrors/help/brew.git">https://lug.ustc.edu.cn/wiki/mirrors/help/brew.git</a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><a href="https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/help/homebrew/">https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/help/homebrew/</a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>Mac 开启第三方显示器 HiDPI</title>
		<link>https://butou.ma/2019/01/21/hackintosh-%e9%bb%91%e8%8b%b9%e6%9e%9c%e7%ac%ac%e4%b8%89%e6%96%b9%e6%98%be%e7%a4%ba%e5%99%a8%e5%bc%80%e5%90%af-hidpi/</link>
		<pubDate>Mon, 21 Jan 2019 15:35:28 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[mabutou]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://butou.ma/?p=358</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:quote -->
<blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p><strong><em>update: 发现另一个脚本写的更好</em></strong></p><p><a href="https://github.com/xzhih/one-key-hidpi/blob/master/README-zh.md">https://github.com/xzhih/one-key-hidpi/blob/master/README-zh.md</a></p></blockquote>
<!-- /wp:quote -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>基本上有三种方法</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:list {"ordered":true} -->
<ol><li>用 SwitchResX 软件开启，软件收费，且使用上并不方便。</li><li>在线生成对应配置文件，手动添加到对应文件夹。详细步骤见地址：https://comsysto.github.io/Display-Override-PropertyList-File-Parser-and-Generator-with-HiDPI-Support-For-Scaled-Resolutions/</li><li><strong>推荐：用专门的脚本生成并添加对应分辨率的配置文件。github 地址：https://github.com/syscl/Enable-HiDPI-OSX</strong></li></ol>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3>使用脚本开启步骤：</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>下载脚本</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:code -->
<pre class="wp-block-code"><code>curl -o ~/enable-HiDPI.sh https://raw.githubusercontent.com/syscl/Enable-HiDPI-OSX/master/enable-HiDPI.sh</code></pre>
<!-- /wp:code -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>更改权限</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:code -->
<pre class="wp-block-code"><code>chmod +x ~/enable-HiDPI.sh</code></pre>
<!-- /wp:code -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>运行</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:code -->
<pre class="wp-block-code"><code>~/enable-HiDPI.sh</code></pre>
<!-- /wp:code -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>重启后生效，使用 RDM 软件快速更改分辨率。</li><li>RDM下载地址: http://avi.alkalay.net/software/RDM/</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":4} -->
<h4>注意：</h4>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>需提前关闭系统的 SIP。</li><li>在 recovery mode 下用终端执行 csrutil disable 即可关闭。设置好 HiDPI 后同样步骤执行 csrutil enable 开启。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>碎片化信息流的聚合与输出 Rsshub + Reeder + Notion</title>
		<link>https://butou.ma/2019/02/15/%e7%a2%8e%e7%89%87%e5%8c%96%e4%bf%a1%e6%81%af%e6%b5%81%e7%9a%84%e8%81%9a%e5%90%88%e4%b8%8e%e8%be%93%e5%87%ba-rsshub-reeder-notion/</link>
		<pubDate>Fri, 15 Feb 2019 10:51:53 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[mabutou]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://butou.ma/?p=367</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><em><strong>19.10.05 update:</strong></em></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>1. 之前在服务器端部署的 <em>ttrss</em> 用一段时间后感觉太臃肿，已更换为轻量级的 <strong><em>Miniflux</em></strong>，直接用 <em>Docker</em> 部署在 <em>nas</em> 上的。支持<strong> <em>Reeder</em></strong> ，安装过程也更简单。</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>     <em>  </em><a href="https://github.com/miniflux/miniflux"><em>https://github.com/miniflux/miniflux</em></a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>2. 迫于 <strong><em>Typora</em></strong> 一直没有 <em>iOS</em> 端，笔记应用迁移到 <em><strong>Notion</strong></em> ，目前有教育优惠，用教育版邮箱注册直接免费。</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>3. <strong><em>Typora</em></strong> 里 md 文件有点多。迁移到 <em><strong>Notion</strong></em> 时，直接导入会造成 md 文件内引用的本地图片丢失。所以先用命令行工具 <strong><em>pandoc</em></strong> 批量转换为 docx 格式文件。再导入 <em><strong>Notion</strong></em>。<strong><em>pandoc</em></strong> 转换文档时可以指定 css 文件进行样式渲染。</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>4. 由于 md 文件散布在不同文件夹，写了个 bash 脚本进行批量汇总及转换。</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>汇总脚本详情见博文：<em><a href="https://butou.ma/2019/09/18/macos-小脚本-批量复制指定目录下特定类型文件" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">https://butou.ma/2019/09/18/macos-小脚本-批量复制指定目录下特定类型文件</a> </em></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>汇总+转换+保留文件夹层级功能脚本点此下载：<a href="https://butou.ma/pandoc.sh"><em>pandoc.sh</em></a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":660} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Screen-Shot-2019-10-05-at-18.23.05-1024x739.png" alt="" class="wp-image-660"/><figcaption>Notion 界面简洁，功能也挺强</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><em>19.08.14 update:</em></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>1. 文内提到的 RSSHub 的开发者已开发了对应的 Chrome 扩展，可以直接检测页面是否支持 RSS，并一键订阅到阅读器。<a href="https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub-Radar">https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub-Radar</a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>2. RSS 阅读器 Inoreader 转为付费的 Reeder 4。并链接到服务器端部署的 ttrss（开源的，支持过滤器）。</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>3. 笔记应用 Trilium 已放弃，转移到 Mac 端的 Typora，配合Google Drive 进行 markdown 文件和图片文件同步。</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><img class="wp-image-594" style="width: 600px;" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Screen-Shot-2019-08-14-at-19.51.19.png" alt=""></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>正文：</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center"><em><strong>“世间好物不坚牢 彩云易散琉璃碎”</strong></em></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<p class="md-end-block" style="text-align: left;" contenteditable="true"><span class="" style="color: #000000;">美好的事物不能永恒存在，自然状态下世间万物总是会从有序到无序，为何如此?</span></p>
<p class="md-end-block" contenteditable="true"><span style="color: #000000;">根据热力学第二定律，封闭系统最终都会趋向混乱度最大的状态，除非外部注入能量。</span></p>
<p class="md-end-block" contenteditable="true"><span style="color: #000000;">也就是说如果没有外力介入，<span class=""><strong>事物永远向着更混乱的状态发展</strong></span><span class="">。</span></span></p>
<p class="md-end-block" contenteditable="true"><span class="" style="color: #000000;">衡量混乱程度的指标叫熵。一种悲观假设是当熵的量增加到极限，宇宙会进入热寂，到达虚无。</span></p>
<p class="md-end-block" contenteditable="true"><span class="" style="color: #000000;">为了让一个系统保持有序，我们必须付出额外代价。注入外部能量来抵抗熵的增加。</span></p>
<p class="md-end-block" contenteditable="true"><span class="" style="color: #000000;">互联网让获取信息的渠道爆发性增长，其中伴随着大量噪音信息。如果不进行筛选和取舍，信噪比会逐步降低。最终吸收的大部份都是垃圾。</span></p>
<p class="md-end-block" contenteditable="true"><span class="" style="color: #000000;">身处比特洪流，未免时有迷茫。</span></p>
<p class="md-end-block" contenteditable="true"><span class="" style="color: #000000;">本文是个人面对这种情形的一种尝试，供参考。</span></p>
<h2>输入</h2>
<p>我平时获取信息的主要渠道有：</p>
<ol start="">
<li>微博</li>
<li>Twitter</li>
<li>Youtube</li>
<li>V2ex</li>
<li>Instagram</li>
<li>微信公众号（过于封闭，已基本放弃）</li>
<li>各种播客</li>
<li>各种博主的个人博客（主要 IT 领域有几十个）</li>
<li>国内外科技网站：如 少数派、Endgnet 等</li>
<li>Telegram 各种群（垃圾信息挺多，偶尔看）</li>
</ol>
<h3>聚合方案</h3>
<p>使用 Rsshub +Inoreader 将各种渠道的关键信息筛选后汇总。</p>
<p>以上渠道除了博客和新闻网站，基本不提供原生rss订阅。</p>
<p>所以得自己动手。</p>
<h4>第一步 制作 RSS 源</h4>
<ul>
<li>RSSHub 是一个轻量、易于扩展的 RSS 生成器, 可以给各种奇奇怪怪的内容生成 RSS 订阅源。
<ul>
<li>github地址：<a class="url" href="https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>主要功能是将一些本来不提供 RSS 的信息源制作成 RSS源。比如微博和 Instagram。</li>
<li>已部署至个人服务器，欢迎使用： <a class="url" href="http://rsshub.mabutou.me" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://rsshub.mabutou.me</a></li>
<li>使用方法很简单参考官方文档：<a class="url" href="https://docs.rsshub.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://docs.rsshub.app</a></li>
</ul>
<p>例：比如制作 木遥 微博的订阅源</p>
<ol start="">
<li>打开目标微博主页</li>
<li>打开网页开发工具，控制台输入 $CONFIG.oid</li>
</ol>
<p><img title="" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/1bb80-006tNc79gy1fz7o3iecajj31hc0u0doc.jpg" alt=""></p>
<ol start="">
<li>复制得到的用户id 1400854834，拼接成对应 url ：<a class="url" href="http://rsshub.mabutou.me/weibo/user/1400854834" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">http://rsshub.mabutou.me/weibo/user/1400854834</a></li>
<li>浏览器如能成功访问此网址，则对应的 RSS 源就生成成功了。</li>
</ol>
<p><img title="" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/60a2c-006tNc79gy1fz7o46nbxqj31hc0u0ag9.jpg" alt=""></p>
<h4>注：有些渠道比较简单，如instagram。直接用id拼接成对应rss地址即可。</h4>
<p><em>以长泽雅美 ?masami_nagasawa为例：https://rsshub.mabutou.me/instagram/user/masami_nagasawa</em></p>
<h4>第二步 订阅和阅读 RSS</h4>
<ul>
<li>rss客户端有很多款，推荐inoreader</li>
<li>inoreader 是一款很优秀的 RSS 阅读客户端。
<ul>
<li>提供网页端和移动端。</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>即使免费用户也有很完善的体验。
<ul>
<li>缺点是免费版不支持过滤，可通过 rsshub 增加 url 过滤参数实现，参考使用文档。</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>地址： <a class="url" href="https://www.inoreader.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://www.inoreader.com</a></li>
<li>将第一步制作好的 RSS 地址添加进去就行。</li>
<li>很多个人博客和媒体网站都原生提供 RSS ，不用自己制作。</li>
</ul>
<p><img title="" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/85039-006tNc79gy1fz7ocdkas1j30sc0fmq3n.jpg" alt=""></p>
<h4>最终效果</h4>
<p><img title="" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/2174f-006tNc79gy1fz7odibpixj31hc0u0jwz.jpg" alt=""></p>
<h4>备注1</h4>
<ul>
<li>可配合 chrome 插件 Easy-to-RSS 直接获取或生成当前页面的 RSS 地址。</li>
<li>安装地址 <a class="url" href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/easy-to-rss/hbcmpkcpbnecinpngdnfbnknfkdpdfli" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/easy-to-rss/hbcmpkcpbnecinpngdnfbnknfkdpdfli</a></li>
<li>github：<a class="url" href="https://github.com/idealclover/Easy-to-RSS" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://github.com/idealclover/Easy-to-RSS</a></li>
</ul>
<ol start="">
<li>如果该网站自带RSS，Easy-to-RSS将获取该网站自带RSS</li>
<li>如果该网站被<a href="https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub">RSSHub</a>收录，Easy-to-RSS将获取该网站在RSSHub中的地址：</li>
</ol>
<ul>
<li>安装好后最好在配置页面把服务器地址改成自己的。</li>
</ul>
<p><img title="" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/c537f-006tNc79gy1fz7p0ogcwij30n208kwej.jpg" alt=""></p>
<p><img title="" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/afe2d-006tNc79gy1fz7p3jhharj31hc0u0tey.jpg" alt=""></p>
<h4>备注2</h4>
<ul>
<li>Inoreader 可与 <a class="url" href="http://reabble.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">http://reabble.com/</a> 联动，实现在kindle上阅读的同时重新排版。</li>
<li>reabble本质上是通过登录 Inoreader 帐号，获取到里面的内容后进行二次排版，专门针对电子墨水屏设备优化。</li>
<li>效果如图：<img title="" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/6a559-006tNc79gy1fz7pphojawj30ts148gm9.jpg" alt=""></li>
</ul>
<h2>输出</h2>
<p>信息流里有些值得记录的信息，需要手动进行整理与归档。方便查阅或回顾。</p>
<ul>
<li>以前的办法：</li>
</ul>
<ol start="">
<li>加浏览器书签（缺点明显，保存的只是链接，有失效风险）。</li>
<li>用笔记软件记录。</li>
</ol>
<ul>
<li>尝试过各类笔记应用，都不太满意。</li>
<li>印象笔记</li>
<li>优点：用户量大，可以跟很多第三方应用联动。</li>
<li>缺点：软件臃肿，免费用户流量限制，设备数限制。　</li>
<li>onenote</li>
<li>优点：编辑功能强大，排版自由度高。</li>
<li>缺点：同步很不稳定。</li>
<li>notion</li>
<li>界面美观。编辑功能比较有特色。</li>
<li>导入与迁移不方便。</li>
<li>还用过一些，反正都不喜欢。核心缺点都是不能方便的备份数据为通用格式。</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li class="md-end-block" contenteditable="true"><span class="">后来转向开源的个人wiki系统。主流的那几个全都试了下，不是太简陋就是太复杂，易用性很一般。</span></li>
</ul>
<p class="md-end-block" contenteditable="true"><strong>最终用的是 Trilium&nbsp;<span class="md-link"><a href="https://github.com/zadam/trilium">https://github.com/zadam/trilium</a></span></strong></p>
<p>一款开源知识库软件。</p>
<ul class="ul-list" data-mark="-">
<li class="md-list-item md-focus-container">
<p class="md-end-block md-focus" contenteditable="true"><span class="md-expand">界面简洁</span></p>
</li>
<li class="md-list-item">
<p class="md-end-block" contenteditable="true">支持导入导出各种格式笔记。html markdown等</p>
</li>
<li class="md-list-item">
<p class="md-end-block" contenteditable="true">支持印象笔记导入</p>
</li>
<li class="md-list-item">
<p class="md-end-block" contenteditable="true">无限笔记层级</p>
</li>
<li class="md-list-item">
<p class="md-end-block" contenteditable="true">有客户端</p>
</li>
<li class="md-list-item">
<p class="md-end-block" contenteditable="true">支持部署到本地电脑或个人服务器，然后通过浏览器访问</p>
</li>
<li class="md-list-item">
<p class="md-end-block" contenteditable="true"><span class="">本地数据可与服务器保持同步。</span></p>
</li>
<li class="md-list-item">
<p class="md-end-block" contenteditable="true"><span class="">有帐号系统（但较弱）</span></p>
</li>
<li class="md-list-item">
<p class="md-end-block" contenteditable="true">编辑模式支持各种代码格式</p>
</li>
<li class="md-list-item">
<p class="md-end-block md-focus" contenteditable="true">支持自定义主题</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p class="md-end-block" contenteditable="true"><span class="md-image md-img-loaded" contenteditable="false" data-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/2d89b-006tKfTcgy1g07akkwhs2j31hc0u00xv.jpg"><img class="aligncenter" title="" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/2d89b-006tKfTcgy1g07akkwhs2j31hc0u00xv.jpg"></span></p>
<h2 class="md-end-block md-heading md-focus" contenteditable="true">检索</h2>
<p class="md-end-block" contenteditable="true"><span class="">应对"知识爆炸"，大脑只需记住核心的知识点，舍弃边缘的知识点。</span></p>
<p class="md-end-block" contenteditable="true"><span class="">碎片化信息流获取的信息大多是边缘知识，不需要刻意记忆，在需要的时候临时通过搜索引擎或者个人 wiki 检索就行（trlium 有全文搜索功能）。</span></p>
<p class="md-end-block" contenteditable="true"><span class="">通过以上步骤的循环积累，个人知识库会逐渐成体系，能大幅增强检索边缘化知识的效率。</span></p>

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>在这个变幻的世界，为避免思维僵化，我们需要走出舒适区不断引入新的知识维度，理解很多看似矛盾对立的现实，最终穿越生活的迷雾构建属于自己的多维度思维模型。</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>道阻且长,行则将至。各位共勉。﻿</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><br></p>

					<item>
		<title>macOS 玄学 bug — 音频输出异常+切换左桌面快捷键失灵（&quot;Move left a space&quot; shortcuts not working）</title>
		<link>https://butou.ma/2019/03/09/macos-%e7%8e%84%e5%ad%a6-bug-%e9%9f%b3%e9%a2%91%e8%be%93%e5%87%ba%e5%bc%82%e5%b8%b8%e5%88%87%e6%8d%a2%e5%b7%a6%e6%a1%8c%e9%9d%a2%e5%bf%ab%e6%8d%b7%e9%94%ae%e5%a4%b1%e7%81%b5%ef%bc%88move/</link>
		<pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2019 04:58:11 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[mabutou]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://butou.ma/?p=449</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>我的系统版本：10.13.5</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>音频输出异常</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:list {"ordered":true} -->
<ol><li>平时正常，每次连接一款蓝牙耳机后，如果打开多个在输出音频的应用，暂停其中一个，其他应用的声音也会消失。</li><li>偶尔出现浏览器视频播放失败，听歌软件无法播放（我用的网易云）。</li></ol>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>解决方法：</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>启动终端，输入命令:</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><g class="gr_ gr_8 gr-alert gr_spell gr_inline_cards gr_run_anim ContextualSpelling" id="8" data-gr-id="8">sudo</g> <g class="gr_ gr_9 gr-alert gr_spell gr_inline_cards gr_run_anim ContextualSpelling" id="9" data-gr-id="9">killall</g> <g class="gr_ gr_7 gr-alert gr_spell gr_inline_cards gr_run_anim ContextualSpelling ins-del multiReplace" id="7" data-gr-id="7">coreaudiod</g></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>回车即可 (可能需要输入密码)</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>切换桌面快捷键失灵</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:list {"ordered":true} -->
<ol><li>设置选项里可以将切换快捷键（Mission Control）设置为其他组合键，如Ctrl + 1 。但是如果其他快捷键设置过同样的组合键，即使没有激活，也会导致左切换快捷键失效（Move left a space），神奇的是右切换不受影响。</li></ol>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:html -->
<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter is-resized"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-2304" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/006tKfTcgy1g0wg1da4stj30yi0u0q5k-1.jpg" width="1242" height="1080" alt="" /></figure></div>
<!-- /wp:html -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>解决方法：</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>先将其他一样的快捷键设置为另外的组合</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>启动终端输入下面命令，回车即可</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>killall Dock</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>「视频」北岛朗诵《歧路行》之序曲</title>
		<link>https://butou.ma/2019/04/20/%e5%8c%97%e5%b2%9b%e6%9c%97%e8%af%b5%e3%80%8a%e6%ad%a7%e8%b7%af%e9%9a%be%e3%80%8b%e4%b9%8b%e5%ba%8f%e6%9b%b2/</link>
		<pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2019 21:28:43 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[mabutou]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://butou.ma/?p=477</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3>翻到16年的一段旧视频，单向空间的活动上北岛朗诵长诗《歧路行》。</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>添加字幕后上传到了 youtube 和 bilibili</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>时间：2016年7月2日</li><li>地点：北京 单向空间书店</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>youtube链接：<a href="https://youtu.be/hkApNJDLltQ">https://youtu.be/hkApNJDLltQ</a>　　</li><li>B站链接：<a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/av49868462/">https://www.bilibili.com/video/av49868462/</a></li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":4} -->
<h4>第一句没录上：</h4>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:quote -->
<blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p>为什么此刻到远古<br>历史逆向而行　</p></blockquote>
<!-- /wp:quote -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":4} -->
<h4>他对在座的读者说：</h4>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:quote -->
<blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p>“我在不同的人生阶段，遭遇了不同的问题。在座的朋友们，年轻的朋友们，你们也会有面临各种各样的问题。我觉得这个时代，也面临着很大的问题。你们要找到一个新的语言，找到一种新的可能性。”</p></blockquote>
<!-- /wp:quote -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>活动结束买了本《在天涯》。</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":178} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/1286186379952447850-1024x769.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-178"/></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":478} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/2016-07-02-11.11.50-1-819x1024.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-478"/></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->]]></content:encoded>

		<wp:meta_key><![CDATA[_edit_last]]></wp:meta_key>
		<wp:meta_value><![CDATA[1]]></wp:meta_value>

					<item>
		<title>如何在不同音乐平台间迁移歌单（Spotify Apple Music 网易云等）</title>
		<link>https://butou.ma/2019/08/08/%e5%a6%82%e4%bd%95%e5%9c%a8%e4%b8%8d%e5%90%8c%e9%9f%b3%e4%b9%90%e5%b9%b3%e5%8f%b0%e9%97%b4%e8%bf%81%e7%a7%bb%e6%ad%8c%e5%8d%95%ef%bc%88spotify-apple-music-%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e4%ba%91%e7%ad%89%ef%bc%89/</link>
		<pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2019 20:58:34 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[mabutou]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://butou.ma/?p=553</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>点击下载觉哥歌单文本文件（共365首）：<a href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/jueSpotifyPlaylist.csv">jueSpotifyPlaylist.csv</a> </p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:quote -->
<blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p><strong>起因：刷微博看到黄觉分享了一个Spotify歌单二维码，发现评论里好多人没用过 Spotify。反正睡不着，顺手写篇相关教程</strong>。</p><cite><img class="wp-image-559" style="width: 150px;" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/截屏-2019-08-08-04.26.48.png" alt=""></cite></blockquote>
<!-- /wp:quote -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>我各种音乐平台都用过，其中网易云重度用户，累计听歌量两万三</li><li><img class="wp-image-565" style="width: 250px;" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/IMG_2962.png" alt=""></li><li>但网易云在 iPhone 上不能在锁屏后用 Siri 直接唤醒放歌（对 AirPods 支持也不行），故最近转移到Apple Music了。（转移了六千首过去）</li><li><img class="wp-image-558" style="width: 250px;" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/image.png" alt=""></li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>也为了防止单一平台版权原因下架，系统研究了一下各平台的迁移方法</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:quote -->
<blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p><strong>先写Spotify转Apple Music，网易云转Apple Music复杂些有空再更新。</strong><em><strong>（其余QQ音乐/虾米音乐之类都比较简单，不一定写了）</strong></em></p></blockquote>
<!-- /wp:quote -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":1} -->
<h1> Spotify 迁移至 Apple Music</h1>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>以觉哥的歌单为例，先把二维码解析为链接<ul><li>先用 Spotify 手机端扫描微博那张图，用右上角自带分享功能得到歌单链接：<a href="https://open.spotify.com/user/huangjue6766/playlist/2lfNXg1139huYYskKclWjD?si=whfaAAhjROihSAOYbykDOw">https://open.spotify.com/user/huangjue6766/playlist/2lfNXg1139huYYskKclWjD?si=whfaAAhjROihSAOYbykDOw</a></li></ul></li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>打开 tunemymusic 网站，网址 <a href="https://www.tunemymusic.com/zh-cn/">https://www.tunemymusic.com/zh-cn/</a></li><li>点击开始，选择来源为 Spotify</li><li><img class="wp-image-554" style="width: 600px;" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/image-20190808040441985.png" alt=""></li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li><strong>上面的链接贴进去</strong></li><li><img class="wp-image-556" style="width: 600px;" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/image-20190808040609080.png" alt=""></li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li><strong>然后按照提示，点下一步，选择目的地为Apple Music</strong></li><li><strong>这一步需要弹到Apple网站登录授权（注意授权完成后，这个界面不会自动响应，需要手动再点击下中间这个按钮）</strong></li><li><img class="wp-image-555" style="width: 600px;" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/image-20190808040853832.png" alt=""></li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li><strong>最后一步，点开始移动，就能一键完成歌单迁移，进度条往后走完后，会提示失败了几首并列出来</strong></li><li><img class="wp-image-557" style="width: 600px;" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Xnip2019-08-08_03-03-06-e1565214414639.jpg" alt=""></li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:quote -->
<blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p><strong>注：</strong></p><p><strong>选择导入源时，也可以直接导入文本文件</strong></p><p><strong>这个网站还支持其他一些平台，步骤都基本一样</strong></p></blockquote>
<!-- /wp:quote -->]]></content:encoded>
		<excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[]]></excerpt:encoded>

					<item>
		<title>个人 Chrome 扩展推荐</title>
		<link>https://butou.ma/2019/09/11/%e4%b8%aa%e4%ba%ba-chrome-%e6%89%a9%e5%b1%95%e6%8e%a8%e8%8d%90/</link>
		<pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2019 11:11:04 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[mabutou]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://butou.ma/?p=620</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:quote -->
<blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p>第一次使用谷歌浏览器是刚上高中时，距现在已有十年了。<br>自从知道 Chrome 有自己的应用商店可以安装各种功能的扩展后，就基本没换过其他浏览器了。<br>十年间用过无数扩展，感觉有必要写篇文章推荐下最终留下来的这些。<br><strong>某些扩展功能比较冷门，下面只介绍比较通用的。</strong><br><strong>Tampermonkey 油猴扩展作为脚本管理器比较特殊，会单独写一篇进行介绍和推荐对应的脚本。</strong></p></blockquote>
<!-- /wp:quote -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>所有扩展截图（<a href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/IMG_6324AB00274A-1.jpeg">查看大图</a>）</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:image {"align":"center","id":621} -->
<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/IMG_6324AB00274A-1-248x1024.jpeg" alt="" class="wp-image-621"/></figure></div>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>必装扩展推荐（点击名称可跳转到应用商店页面）</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/extensity/jjmflmamggggndanpgfnpelongoepncg">Extensity</a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>管理扩展的扩展。</li><li>扩展装的太多后，会拖慢电脑运行速度，某些扩展只是特定场景使用，所以有必要用一个管理器进行管理。</li><li>界面简洁，支持分组和一键关闭或启用单个及某组扩展。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:image {"align":"center","id":622,"width":183,"height":352} -->
<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter is-resized"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Screen-Shot-2019-09-11-at-17.24.12-531x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-622" width="183" height="352"/></figure></div>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/tampermonkey/dhdgffkkebhmkfjojejmpbldmpobfkfo">Tampermonkey</a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>专门管理和运行 JS 脚本的扩展，非常强大。</li><li>需配合各种脚本使用，所以会单写一篇介绍。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/dark-reader/eimadpbcbfnmbkopoojfekhnkhdbieeh">Dark Reader</a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>可以为那些不支持黑暗模式的网站自动生成黑暗模式配色，也可以在 UI 界面自定义黑暗效果。</li><li>专业用户还可以编辑 css 文件针对不同网站进行定制。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ublock-origin/cjpalhdlnbpafiamejdnhcphjbkeiagm">uBlock Origin</a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>网页广告拦截器。</li><li>优点是内存和CPU占用低（相比于其他同类扩展）。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/imagus/immpkjjlgappgfkkfieppnmlhakdmaab">Imagus</a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>看图利器</li><li>鼠标悬停在图片上时，会自动弹出分辨率更高的原图，不需要额外点击。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/onetab/chphlpgkkbolifaimnlloiipkdnihall">OneTab</a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>打开太多的标签页时，单击OneTab图标，一键将所有标签页转换成一个列表。</li><li>需要再次访问这些标签页时，也可以单独或全部一键恢复。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/xstyle/hncgkmhphmncjohllpoleelnibpmccpj">xStyle</a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>可以为各种网站创建 css 文件进行页面样式定制</li><li>同类软件有Stylus，这款UI更现代些。</li><li>样式文件可以去专门网站安装，有很多网友共享的<ul><li>比如 <a href="https://userstyles.org">https://userstyles.org</a></li></ul></li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/im-a-gentleman/afjaicccalbbickikgdegaihmajaidpd">I'm a Gentleman</a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>鼠标在图片上拖拽，就能保存图片到本地。比右键点保存更快。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/simpread-reader-view/ijllcpnolfcooahcekpamkbidhejabll">简悦 - SimpRead</a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>排除多余元素，将网页文本重排，瞬间进入沉浸式阅读模式。</li><li>类似 Safari 的阅读模式,但更强大。</li><li>支持各种主题。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><a href="[https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/%E4%BA%91%E7%9B%98%E4%B8%87%E8%83%BD%E9%92%A5%E5%8C%99/anlllmnpjodopgbkbpnghnjlelnogfjc](https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/云盘万能钥匙/anlllmnpjodopgbkbpnghnjlelnogfjc)">云盘万能钥匙</a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>自动填写百度网盘 &amp; 蓝奏云提取密码。 </li><li>自动检测百度网盘 &amp; 蓝奏云分享链接的状态是否有效。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/search-the-current-site/jliolpcnkmolaaecncdfeofombdekjcp">Search the current site (站内搜索)</a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>使用 Google 等搜索引擎提供当前浏览网站的站内搜索功能。</li><li>其实就是省去了自己填写 site: 关键词的作用。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><a href="[https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/pakku%EF%BC%9A%E5%93%94%E5%93%A9%E5%93%94%E5%93%A9%E5%BC%B9%E5%B9%95%E8%BF%87%E6%BB%A4%E5%99%A8/jklfcpboamajpiikgkbjcnnnnooefbhh](https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/pakku：哔哩哔哩弹幕过滤器/jklfcpboamajpiikgkbjcnnnnooefbhh)">pakku：哔哩哔哩弹幕过滤器</a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>过滤B站(bilibili.com)的刷屏弹幕。</li><li>将同样内容弹幕合并。</li><li>进度条上显示弹幕密度图。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/view-image/jpcmhcelnjdmblfmjabdeclccemkghjk">View Image</a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>重新添加 Google 图片结果页面的“查看图片”和“以图搜图”按钮。<ul><li>这两个按钮以前一直有，后来由于版权考虑，Google 给去掉了。</li></ul></li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><a href="[https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/%E4%BA%AC%E4%BB%B7%E4%BF%9D-%E4%BA%AC%E4%B8%9C%E4%BB%B7%E4%BF%9D%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B/gfgkebiommjpiaomalcbfefimhhanlfd](https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/京价保-京东价保助手/gfgkebiommjpiaomalcbfefimhhanlfd)">京价保 - 京东价保助手</a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>自动为你申请京东价格保护，自动签到领京豆、钢镚。</li><li>很实用，因为京东的价格保护不是自动触发的，需要自己手动去申请</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><a href="[https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/%E7%8C%AB%E6%8A%93/jfedfbgedapdagkghmgibemcoggfppbb](https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/猫抓/jfedfbgedapdagkghmgibemcoggfppbb)">猫抓</a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>网页媒体嗅探工具,比如 mp3 文件，视频文件。</li><li>但适用网页不多，需和更强大的脚本配合。<ul><li>比如 SaveFrom.net 提供的脚本，支持各类网站 YouTube Instagram等（此脚本需配合油猴使用）。</li></ul></li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":1} -->
<h1>英语学习类</h1>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/grammarly-for-chrome/kbfnbcaeplbcioakkpcpgfkobkghlhen">Grammarly for Chrome</a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>著名语法纠正软件的 Chrome 版。</li><li>能监测输入框内容的语法错误或表达瑕疵，并提供修改建议。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><a href="[https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/%E6%B2%99%E6%8B%89%E6%9F%A5%E8%AF%8D-%E8%81%9A%E5%90%88%E8%AF%8D%E5%85%B8%E5%88%92%E8%AF%8D%E7%BF%BB%E8%AF%91/cdonnmffkdaoajfknoeeecmchibpmkmg](https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/沙拉查词-聚合词典划词翻译/cdonnmffkdaoajfknoeeecmchibpmkmg)">Saladict 沙拉查词</a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>界面美观，功能强大。</li><li>涵盖中英日韩法德西语，支持划词操作、网页翻译、生词本、PDF查词。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/online-dictionary-helper/lppjdajkacanlmpbbcdkccjkdbpllajb">在线词典助手</a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>查词功能上比沙拉查词弱。</li><li>特色功能是支持连接桌面端 Anki 客户端，实现一键将单词制作成 Anki 卡片。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/words-discoverer-expand-y/noncaeikjgpbdeoocblijjgegnobogib">单词发现者</a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>高亮显示网页上的英文生词。</li><li>可以直接导入熟词库。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>先写这些，剩下的在文首截图里有，可以根据截图上的自带介绍判断是否符合自己需要。</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->]]></content:encoded>

					</item>
					<item>
		<title>macOS 小脚本-批量复制指定目录下特定类型文件</title>
		<link>https://butou.ma/2019/09/18/macos-%e5%b0%8f%e8%84%9a%e6%9c%ac-%e6%89%b9%e9%87%8f%e5%a4%8d%e5%88%b6%e6%8c%87%e5%ae%9a%e7%9b%ae%e5%bd%95%e4%b8%8b%e7%89%b9%e5%ae%9a%e7%b1%bb%e5%9e%8b%e6%96%87%e4%bb%b6/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2019 16:46:22 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[mabutou]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://butou.ma/?p=635</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:quote -->
<blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p>github: <a href="https://github.com/mabutou/macOS_copyScript">https://github.com/mabutou/macOS_copyScript</a></p></blockquote>
<!-- /wp:quote -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3 id="%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%BA%E6%99%AF">使用场景：</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>比如我想将某个目录下的几百个 .md 文件（分布在数十个多级子文件夹内），全部集中到一个单独的文件夹内。</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>Linux 系统上可以用一条 find 和 cp 组合命令直接完成。</li><li>然而 macOS 上命令貌似不太兼容，就写了个小脚本，只在 Mac 上试了，Linux 估计也适用。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3 id="%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95">使用方法：</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>按个人需求修改下方脚本内对应的路径和格式名。创建成 sh 文件放到对应目录。比如叫&nbsp;<a href="http://copyscript.sh/">copyScript.sh</a>。</li><li>若要保留文件夹层级，只是为了过滤文件。则删除倒数 7、8 行注释，同时注释掉倒数第 5 行。</li><li>使用 sh&nbsp;<a href="http://copyscript.sh/">copyScript.sh</a>&nbsp;命令执行即可。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:code -->
<pre class="wp-block-code"><code>#!/bin/bash
#修改IFS变量，将分割字段的字符改为换行符，默认IFS变量含有空格，后续命令会识别不了含有空格的文件夹和文件名
IFS=$'\n'
#递归过滤当前目录及子目录的所有指定格式文件，默认为md，按需修改
head_files=`find ./ -name "*.md" -print`
#设置目标文件夹
des_dir="/Users/XXX/Downloads/md"
echo $des_dir
#如果没有对应目标文件夹就创建
[ -d $des_dir ] || mkdir -p $des_dir &amp;> /dev/null
#按行读取文件路径
for file in $head_files
do
source_dir=${file#./}
echo $source_dir;
#是否保留文件夹层级
#[ -d $des_dir$source_dir ] || mkdir -p $des_dir$source_dir
#cp -p "$file" $des_dir$source_dir
#执行复制命令
cp -p "$file" $des_dir
((file_count++))
done
echo "复制完毕?"
echo "文件总数：${file_count} ?"</code></pre>
<!-- /wp:code -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>

					</item>
					<item>
		<title>机械键盘换轴记 — FILCO MINILA AIR 67键 红轴</title>
		<link>https://butou.ma/2019/10/05/%e6%9c%ba%e6%a2%b0%e9%94%ae%e7%9b%98%e6%8d%a2%e8%bd%b4%e8%ae%b0-filco-minila-air-67%e9%94%ae-%e7%ba%a2%e8%bd%b4/</link>
		<pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2019 16:22:09 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[mabutou]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://butou.ma/?p=641</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>我目前用的是 filco 的 minila 系列红轴机械键盘（只有蓝牙模式）。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:image {"align":"center","id":652,"width":311,"height":358} -->
<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter is-resized"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Xnip2019-10-05_00-17-05-888x1024.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-652" width="311" height="358"/></figure></div>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li><strong>两年多前买的。前段时间感觉灰尘有点多，把键帽拆下来清了一下灰。几天后发现数字 5 键有点失灵，然而已过两年保修期了。</strong></li><li>上淘宝一看。有对应的维修服务，但感觉邮过去再等店家修好邮回来时间周期太长，还不如自己买工具修。</li><li>一查资料，filco 的轴是焊在电路板上的，需要电烙铁之类的工具，所以顺便网购了一整套工具（新轴也在这家店买的）。这套小工具既能修键盘也能修其他鼠标之类的数码产品。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:image {"align":"center","id":648,"width":321,"height":321} -->
<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter is-resized"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/TB25_SQbchmZKJjSZFPXXc5_XXa_294139046.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-648" width="321" height="321"/></figure></div>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3>维修过程 </h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>先把背面两颗螺丝卸下来。</li><li>螺丝刀对应的是六角的头。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:image {"align":"center","id":646,"width":178,"height":302} -->
<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter is-resized"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Xnip2019-10-04_23-38-35.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-646" width="178" height="302"/></figure></div>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>用撬棒或者撬片之类片状的物体把卡扣撬开，就能卸下后盖。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:image {"align":"center","id":642} -->
<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Xnip2019-10-04_23-33-29-1024x464.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-642"/></figure></div>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>接下来这步要小心，轴体电路板和蓝牙控制板之间是用针式接口连接，要垂直拔掉，拧的幅度别太大，容易拧坏。 </li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:image {"align":"center","id":644,"width":450,"height":340} -->
<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter is-resized"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Xnip2019-10-04_23-33-58-1024x776.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-644" width="450" height="340"/></figure></div>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>分离成功后就能看到整体板子的布局。</li><li>每个轴体有两个针脚跟电路板连接，直接焊接上去的。 </li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:image {"align":"center","id":643,"width":523,"height":368} -->
<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter is-resized"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Xnip2019-10-04_23-35-05.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-643" width="523" height="368"/></figure></div>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>用电烙铁熔化原本的锡。融化过程中可以用吸锡带或者吸锡器辅助。 </li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:image {"align":"center","id":645,"width":279,"height":368} -->
<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter is-resized"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Xnip2019-10-04_23-35-37-777x1024.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-645" width="279" height="368"/></figure></div>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>融化完用拔轴器将坏轴拔下来。 </li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:image {"align":"center","id":647,"width":305,"height":307} -->
<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter is-resized"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mabutou/cdn/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Xnip2019-10-04_23-36-09.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-647" width="305" height="307"/></figure></div>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>焊接上新买的樱桃红轴。 测试是否正常工作，再安装好后盖。 </li><li>有意向购买 filco 键盘的朋友，推荐买蓝牙有线双模版。纯蓝牙版厚度相对略厚。有 USB 接口适用场景更广。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->]]></content:encoded>

							</item>
					<item>
		<title>群晖系统提示硬盘损毁后提取硬盘数据</title>
		<link>https://butou.ma/2019/10/22/%e7%be%a4%e6%99%96%e7%b3%bb%e7%bb%9f%e6%8f%90%e7%a4%ba%e7%a1%ac%e7%9b%98%e6%8d%9f%e6%af%81%e5%90%8e%e6%8f%90%e5%8f%96%e7%a1%ac%e7%9b%98%e6%95%b0%e6%8d%ae/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2019 04:53:58 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[mabutou]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://butou.ma/?p=680</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>群晖系统在安装新硬盘时需要进行硬盘的初始化，支持 ext4 或者 btrfs 两种文件系统。（我用的 brtfs）</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>群晖在检测到硬盘健康状况不太好时，容易提示硬盘损毁，此时在群晖系统内无法读写硬盘内容了。一般重新格式化或者修复下坏道就能继续正常用。</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>此时如果想要先取出其中的文件只能用其他系统。这两种格式都不能直接在 Mac 系统或者 windows 系统里正常读取。</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>不过可以用 Linux 系统读取。</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>以 Ubuntu 为例：</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>使用虚拟机直接装一个 Ubuntu。或者制作u盘启动盘，进入 <em>LiveCD</em> 模式启动电脑。</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>推荐使用虚拟机</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>我用的Mac上的 Parallels，VMware 当然也行。</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>进入系统后打开终端并以 root 身份（sudo -i）执行以下操作：</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li><code>apt-get update</code></li><li><code>apt-get install mdadm lvm2&nbsp;btrfs-prog</code></li><li><code>mdadm -Asf &amp;&amp; vgchange -ay</code></li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>然后在文件管理器内就能看到对应的盘，文件数量少的话，直接手动选择复制就行。</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:quote -->
<blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p><strong>以上步骤随手一谷歌就能在网上找到，以下才是重点。</strong></p></blockquote>
<!-- /wp:quote -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>在文件浏览器里可以直接批量复制，刚开始我是 smb 协议链接到 nas 去，进行远程复制。</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>然而会遇到@开头的文件夹，此时会提示是否跳过，这种文件夹很多，一直点很烦，不点就会卡在那。而且测试后发现，smb 协议速度一般。</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>所以我直接先用 Mac 的 Finder 用 afp 协议链接到 nas，在Ubuntu终端内用 rsync 复制的，直接排除掉@开头文件夹，速度也快很多。</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>命令大概如下，排除掉特殊文件夹。并远程连接到Mac挂载好的nas。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>其中第一个xxx 代表你要复制的文件夹，/Volumes/nas/xxx是nas内的目标文件夹</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>mabutou@192.168.1.100 代表 Mac 的局域网 ssh 用户名和地址（需要提前开启 ssh 功能，系统设置里就能直接打开）</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:code -->
<pre class="wp-block-code"><code>rsync -ruv --progress --exclude='@eaDir' xxx mabutou@192.168.1.100:/Volumes/nas/xxx</code></pre>
<!-- /wp:code -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>然后坐等复制完成就行。</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>

							</item>
					<item>
		<title>解决 vultr 恢复历史快照后，莫名断网问题</title>
		<link>https://butou.ma/2019/10/22/%e8%a7%a3%e5%86%b3-vultr-%e6%81%a2%e5%a4%8d%e5%8e%86%e5%8f%b2%e5%bf%ab%e7%85%a7%e5%90%8e%ef%bc%8c%e8%8e%ab%e5%90%8d%e6%96%ad%e7%bd%91%e9%97%ae%e9%a2%98/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2019 05:43:14 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[mabutou]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://butou.ma/?p=686</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:quote -->
<blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p><strong>这算是vultr机器的老问题了，不明白为啥vultr一直没解决。</strong></p></blockquote>
<!-- /wp:quote -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2><strong>起因</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>之前服务器中了一个俄罗斯的病毒，其实没啥影响，几下解决后，总感觉不舒服可能有其他残留毒素。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>看了下最新的快照列表，中毒前后没什么大的数据更改。干脆直接恢复快照好了。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>经过</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>以前也恢复过很多次快照，很顺利，这次恢复后，ssh直接连不上。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>用 ping 工具测试，发现无论海内还是海外，一片红。那显然是机器出问题了。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>无奈只好进vultr后台用vnc方式登陆。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li><strong>搞半天没解决。一谷歌是vultr老问题了，恢复快照后，偶尔会发生网卡异常。</strong></li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3>需要手动修改下配置文件。</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>这篇文章里有详细分析和解决过程 <a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/52989069">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/52989069</a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Centos 配置文件和Ubuntu/Debian略有不同。</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>手动修改步骤谷歌能找到对应的一堆文章，我就不写了。（主要是懒，有空闲的时候再补上吧）</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>结果</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>这次修复好了，以后还是有几率出现同样问题。</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>所以最好在机器正常时放一个修复脚本再创建快照，免去后顾之忧。快照本身如果没有这个脚本，恢复后遇到断网也是不能直接连到外网下载脚本的。</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>脚本地址：<a href="https://github.com/leitbogioro/fix_deviant_NIC">https://github.com/leitbogioro/fix_deviant_NIC</a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>

		<category domain="post_tag" nicename="%e6%96%ad%e7%bd%91"><![CDATA[断网]]></category>

							</item>
					<item>
		<title>国内主机配置 k8s 的注意事项及如何正确设置代理</title>
		<link>https://butou.ma/2019/11/23/%e5%9b%bd%e5%86%85%e4%b8%bb%e6%9c%ba%e9%85%8d%e7%bd%ae-k8s-%e7%9a%84%e6%b3%a8%e6%84%8f%e4%ba%8b%e9%a1%b9%e5%8f%8a%e5%a6%82%e4%bd%95%e6%ad%a3%e7%a1%ae%e8%ae%be%e7%bd%ae%e4%bb%a3%e7%90%86/</link>
		<pubDate>Sat, 23 Nov 2019 04:36:51 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[mabutou]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://butou.ma/?p=702</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:quote -->
<blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p>最近学习 kubernetes，在公司三台 centos7 服务器上用 kubeadm 部署k8s测试环境。</p><p>过程中有些注意事项，提前避开能节省很多时间。</p></blockquote>
<!-- /wp:quote -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>1. 安装指定 docker 版本</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li> kubeadm 对 docker 版本的支持有限，目前只支持到18.09</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>直接装最新版的会在后面步骤里报错，还得重装一次。 </li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>2.某些教程里使用的是旧版 kubeadm ，对应的 weave 安装命令也是旧版的</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>我装的最新版 kubeadm (1.16)，发现装 weave 时遇到版本问题。</li><li>用下面命令装的 ：</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:code -->
<pre class="wp-block-code"><code>kubectl apply -f "https://cloud.weave.works/k8s/net?k8s-version=$(kubectl version | base64 | tr -d '\n')"  </code></pre>
<!-- /wp:code -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong> 3. 正确设置代理（重要）。 </strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>本来kubeadm部署k8s很简单，但国内无法正常访问 <a href="http://gcr.io">gcr.io</a> 。很多人被拉取 <a href="http://k8s.gcr.io/v2/">gcr.io</a> 镜像时的网络问题卡住。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>linux 下在终端用 setproxy 或 sethttp 命令设置的代理对 docker pull 无效。需要额外设置。</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3>操作步骤</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>创建目录</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:code -->
<pre class="wp-block-code"><code>sudo mkdir -p /etc/systemd/system/docker.service.d</code></pre>
<!-- /wp:code -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>新建文件，走http代理</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:code -->
<pre class="wp-block-code"><code>vim /etc/systemd/system/docker.service.d/http-proxy.conf</code></pre>
<!-- /wp:code -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>内容（ip和端口号根据客户端设置修改）</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:code -->
<pre class="wp-block-code"><code>[Service]
Environment="HTTP_PROXY=http://127.0.0.1:8001/"</code></pre>
<!-- /wp:code -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>刷新更改</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:code -->
<pre class="wp-block-code"><code>sudo systemctl daemon-reload</code></pre>
<!-- /wp:code -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>重新启动Docker</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:code -->
<pre class="wp-block-code"><code>sudo systemctl restart docker</code></pre>
<!-- /wp:code -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>验证配置是否已加载</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:code -->
<pre class="wp-block-code"><code>systemctl show --property=Environment docker</code></pre>
<!-- /wp:code -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>如果生效会显示对应设置参数</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>之后的步骤里就可以 pull <a href="http://gcr.io">gcr.io</a> 上的镜像了。</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:quote -->
<blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p>详细配置参考官网文档：</p><cite><a href="https://docs.docker.com/config/daemon/systemd/">https://docs.docker.com/config/daemon/systemd/</a></cite></blockquote>
<!-- /wp:quote -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>注：如果配置的是局域网内其他机器上运行的代理客户端，需要在对应客户端开启局域网共享功能（某些 GUI 客户端没有这个选项，可以手动在配置文件里将本地监听从 127.0.0.1 改成 0.0.0.0 ）。</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>

Saving the world with meals on wheels. I am the Doctor, and you are the Daleks! I hate yogurt. It's just stuff with bits in. No… It's a thing; it's like a plan, but with more greatness.

I hate yogurt. It's just stuff with bits in. No, I'll fix it. I'm good at fixing rot. Call me the Rotmeister. No, I'm the Doctor. Don't call me the Rotmeister. Aw, you're all Mr. Grumpy Face today. You've swallowed a planet!

		<content:encoded><![CDATA[The way I see it, every life is a pile of good things and bad things.…hey.…the good things don't always soften the bad things; but vice-versa the bad things don't necessarily spoil the good things and make them unimportant.

I'm the Doctor. Well, they call me the Doctor. I don't know why. I call me the Doctor too. I still don't know why. Heh-haa! Super squeaky bum time! You know how I sometimes have really brilliant ideas?

Saving the world with meals on wheels. I am the Doctor, and you are the Daleks! I hate yogurt. It's just stuff with bits in. No… It's a thing; it's like a plan, but with more greatness.

I hate yogurt. It's just stuff with bits in. No, I'll fix it. I'm good at fixing rot. Call me the Rotmeister. No, I'm the Doctor. Don't call me the Rotmeister. Aw, you're all Mr. Grumpy Face today. You've swallowed a planet!

		<content:encoded><![CDATA[The way I see it, every life is a pile of good things and bad things.…hey.…the good things don't always soften the bad things; but vice-versa the bad things don't necessarily spoil the good things and make them unimportant.

I'm the Doctor. Well, they call me the Doctor. I don't know why. I call me the Doctor too. I still don't know why. Heh-haa! Super squeaky bum time! You know how I sometimes have really brilliant ideas?

Saving the world with meals on wheels. I am the Doctor, and you are the Daleks! I hate yogurt. It's just stuff with bits in. No… It's a thing; it's like a plan, but with more greatness.

I hate yogurt. It's just stuff with bits in. No, I'll fix it. I'm good at fixing rot. Call me the Rotmeister. No, I'm the Doctor. Don't call me the Rotmeister. Aw, you're all Mr. Grumpy Face today. You've swallowed a planet!
<h2>Memories Last Forever</h2>

Green, fowl gathering first, firmament. In i. Be. Dry green said first seasons. Called above.

		<title>Stop Wishing Start Doing</title>

		<content:encoded><![CDATA[The way I see it, every life is a pile of good things and bad things.…hey.…the good things don't always soften the bad things; but vice-versa the bad things don't necessarily spoil the good things and make them unimportant.

I'm the Doctor. Well, they call me the Doctor. I don't know why. I call me the Doctor too. I still don't know why. Heh-haa! Super squeaky bum time! You know how I sometimes have really brilliant ideas?

Saving the world with meals on wheels. I am the Doctor, and you are the Daleks! I hate yogurt. It's just stuff with bits in. No… It's a thing; it's like a plan, but with more greatness.

I hate yogurt. It's just stuff with bits in. No, I'll fix it. I'm good at fixing rot. Call me the Rotmeister. No, I'm the Doctor. Don't call me the Rotmeister. Aw, you're all Mr. Grumpy Face today. You've swallowed a planet!
<h2>Memories Last Forever</h2>

Green, fowl gathering first, firmament. In i. Be. Dry green said first seasons. Called above.

					<item>
		<title>Welcome to the Gutenberg Editor</title>
		<link>https://butou.ma/2020/04/04/__trashed-2/</link>
		<pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2020 12:11:47 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[mabutou]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://butou.ma/?p=303</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:cover-image {"url":"https://cldup.com/Fz-ASbo2s3.jpg","align":"wide"} -->
<div class="wp-block-cover-image has-background-dim alignwide" style="background-image:url(https://cldup.com/Fz-ASbo2s3.jpg)"><p class="wp-block-cover-image-text">Of Mountains &amp; Printing Presses</p></div>
<!-- /wp:cover-image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The goal of this new editor is to make adding rich content to WordPress simple and enjoyable. This whole post is composed of <em>pieces of content</em>—somewhat similar to LEGO bricks—that you can move around and interact with. Move your cursor around and you'll notice the different blocks light up with outlines and arrows. Press the arrows to reposition blocks quickly, without fearing about losing things in the process of copying and pasting.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>What you are reading now is a <strong>text block</strong>, the most basic block of all. The text block has its own controls to be moved freely around the post...</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"right"} -->
<p style="text-align:right">... like this one, which is right aligned.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Headings are separate blocks as well, which helps with the outline and organization of your content.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>A Picture is worth a Thousand Words</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Handling images and media with the utmost care is a primary focus of the new editor. Hopefully, you'll find aspects of adding captions or going full-width with your pictures much easier and robust than before.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:image {"align":"center"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter"><img src="https://cldup.com/cXyG__fTLN.jpg" alt="Beautiful landscape"/><figcaption>If your theme supports it, you'll see the "wide" button on the image toolbar. Give it a try.</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Try selecting and removing or editing the caption, now you don't have to be careful about selecting the image or other text by mistake and ruining the presentation.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>The <em>Inserter</em> Tool</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Imagine everything that WordPress can do is available to you quickly and in the same place on the interface. No need to figure out HTML tags, classes, or remember complicated shortcode syntax. That's the spirit behind the inserter—the <code>(+)</code> button you'll see around the editor—which allows you to browse all available content blocks and add them into your post. Plugins and themes are able to register their own, opening up all sort of possibilities for rich editing and publishing.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Go give it a try, you may discover things WordPress can already add into your posts that you didn't know about. Here's a short list of what you can currently find there:</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><li>Text &amp; Headings</li><li>Images &amp; Videos</li><li>Galleries</li><li>Embeds, like YouTube, Tweets, or other WordPress posts.</li><li>Layout blocks, like Buttons, Hero Images, Separators, etc.</li><li>And <em>Lists</em> like this one of course :)</li></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>Visual Editing</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>A huge benefit of blocks is that you can edit them in place and manipulate your content directly. Instead of having fields for editing things like the source of a quote, or the text of a button, you can directly change the content. Try editing the following quote:</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:quote -->
<blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p>The editor will endeavour to create a new page and post building experience that makes writing rich posts effortless, and has “blocks” to make it easy what today might take shortcodes, custom HTML, or “mystery meat” embed discovery.</p><cite>Matt Mullenweg, 2017</cite></blockquote>
<!-- /wp:quote -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The information corresponding to the source of the quote is a separate text field, similar to captions under images, so the structure of the quote is protected even if you select, modify, or remove the source. It's always easy to add it back.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Blocks can be anything you need. For instance, you may want to add a subdued quote as part of the composition of your text, or you may prefer to display a giant stylized one. All of these options are available in the inserter.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:gallery {"columns":2} -->
<ul class="wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped"><li class="blocks-gallery-item"><figure><img src="https://cldup.com/n0g6ME5VKC.jpg" alt=""/></figure></li><li class="blocks-gallery-item"><figure><img src="https://cldup.com/ZjESfxPI3R.jpg" alt=""/></figure></li><li class="blocks-gallery-item"><figure><img src="https://cldup.com/EKNF8xD2UM.jpg" alt=""/></figure></li></ul>
<!-- /wp:gallery -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>You can change the amount of columns in your galleries by dragging a slider in the block inspector in the sidebar.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>Media Rich</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>If you combine the new <strong>wide</strong> and <strong>full-wide</strong> alignments with galleries, you can create a very media rich layout, very quickly:</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:image {"align":"full"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image alignfull"><img src="https://cldup.com/8lhI-gKnI2.jpg" alt="Accessibility is important don't forget image alt attribute"/></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Sure, the full-wide image can be pretty big. But sometimes the image is worth it.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:gallery {"align":"wide"} -->
<ul class="wp-block-gallery alignwide columns-2 is-cropped"><li class="blocks-gallery-item"><figure><img src="https://cldup.com/_rSwtEeDGD.jpg" alt=""/></figure></li><li class="blocks-gallery-item"><figure><img src="https://cldup.com/L-cC3qX2DN.jpg" alt=""/></figure></li></ul>
<!-- /wp:gallery -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The above is a gallery with just two images. It's an easier way to create visually appealing layouts, without having to deal with floats. You can also easily convert the gallery back to individual images again, by using the block switcher.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Any block can opt into these alignments. The embed block has them also, and is responsive out of the box:</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:core-embed/vimeo {"url":"https://vimeo.com/22439234","type":"video","providerNameSlug":"vimeo","align":"wide"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-embed-vimeo alignwide wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-vimeo">
https://vimeo.com/22439234
</figure>
<!-- /wp:core-embed/vimeo -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>You can build any block you like, static or dynamic, decorative or plain. Here's a pullquote block:</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:pullquote -->
<blockquote class="wp-block-pullquote"><p>Code is Poetry</p><cite>The WordPress community</cite></blockquote>
<!-- /wp:pullquote -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center"} -->
<p style="text-align:center"><em>If you want to learn more about how to build additional blocks, or if you are interested in helping with the project, head over to the <a href="https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg">GitHub repository</a>.</em></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:button {"align":"center"} -->
<div class="wp-block-button aligncenter"><a class="wp-block-button__link" href="https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg">Help build Gutenberg</a></div>
<!-- /wp:button -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center"} -->
<p style="text-align:center">Thanks for testing Gutenberg!</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center"} -->
<p style="text-align:center"><img draggable="false" class="emoji" alt="?" src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/2.3/svg/1f44b.svg"/></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>

I'm the Doctor. Well, they call me the Doctor. I don't know why. I call me the Doctor too. I still don't know why. Heh-haa! Super squeaky bum time! You know how I sometimes have really brilliant ideas?

Saving the world with meals on wheels. I am the Doctor, and you are the Daleks! I hate yogurt. It's just stuff with bits in. No… It's a thing; it's like a plan, but with more greatness.

I hate yogurt. It's just stuff with bits in. No, I'll fix it. I'm good at fixing rot. Call me the Rotmeister. No, I'm the Doctor. Don't call me the Rotmeister. Aw, you're all Mr. Grumpy Face today. You've swallowed a planet!

		<title>Becoming a Dragonfly</title>
		<link>https://butou.ma/2016/08/02/becoming-a-dragonfly__trashed/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 02 Aug 2016 18:36:06 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[mabutou]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://themes.pixelwars.org/theblogger/default/?p=46</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[The way I see it, every life is a pile of good things and bad things.…hey.…the good things don't always soften the bad things; but vice-versa the bad things don't necessarily spoil the good things and make them unimportant.

I'm the Doctor. Well, they call me the Doctor. I don't know why. I call me the Doctor too. I still don't know why. Heh-haa! Super squeaky bum time! You know how I sometimes have really brilliant ideas?

Saving the world with meals on wheels. I am the Doctor, and you are the Daleks! I hate yogurt. It's just stuff with bits in. No… It's a thing; it's like a plan, but with more greatness.

I hate yogurt. It's just stuff with bits in. No, I'll fix it. I'm good at fixing rot. Call me the Rotmeister. No, I'm the Doctor. Don't call me the Rotmeister. Aw, you're all Mr. Grumpy Face today. You've swallowed a planet!
